g.text: A Design is a set of buildings
A Balancer is a design that balances items
A Splitter is a design that splits items
A Factory Splitter is a design that splits items to multiple factories
A Valve is a design that manages overflow of items on a belt
A Lab Balancer is a design that balances items to a Research Lab or Gold Vault
description: "Purely decorative, make your factory one of a kind."
description: "Increases the speed of nearby factories while consuming the input items. Effect does not stack with other power plants."
